                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-cyan-400 mb-6 border-b border-dark-700 pb-4" data-en="Custom Commands & Aliases ⌨️">الأوامر المتعددة (Aliases) ⌨️</h2>
                    
                    <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-t-4 border-t-cyan-500 shadow-lg">
